(189, 2, '2014-04-04 12:10:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Though they’ll never admit it, our relationship is the result of a setup by Shawn’s sister, Jenn, and brother-in-law, Russ.  We met in 2009 over the 4<sup>th</sup> of July weekend while visiting Jenn and Russ in Wilmington, NC.  We were both a little cynical; not only is Bert Russ’ childhood best friend, but we were also set to be best man and maid of honor in Jenn and Russ’ wedding the following spring.  It just seemed to be a little too perfect of a situation to really work.\r\n\r\nLater that same year, Shawn accepted a mass invitation Bert sent to several friends to take a trip to Orlando to attend one of the final space shuttle launches.  Though we were still hesitant to initiate a relationship, this trip made us realize we’d regret it if we didn’t give it a shot.  Our relationship survived an initial two and a half years of long distance, between Charlotte, NC and Washington, DC, getting better every day.  We’re both so excited we get to marry our best friend!', 'How We Met', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', '', '', '', '2014-04-04 12:10:49', '2014-04-04 16:10:49', '', 0, 'http://www.shawnandbert.com/?page_id=189', 0, 'page', '', 0),
